import React from "react"
import {
  Flex,
  Divider,
  Avatar,
  Heading,
  Text,
  Box,
  Stack,
  Link,
} from "@chakra-ui/react"

const Sidebar = () => (
  <Box as="aside" w="64" mr="8">
    <Stack spacing="12" align="flex-start">
      <Box>
        <Text fontWeight="bold">Geral</Text>
        <Stack spacing="4" mt="8" align="stretch">
          <Link />
        </Stack>
      </Box>
    </Stack>
  </Box>
)

export default Sidebar
